\end_inset

是区间
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

中的可微函数, 且
\begin_inset Formula $\phi(I)\subset J$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(1) 设
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

上的原函数是
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $F(\phi)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $f(\phi)\phi'$
\end_inset

在区间
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

上的原函数, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int f(\phi(x))\phi^{\prime}(x)dx=\int f(u)du+C=F(\phi(x))+C;
