\begin_layout Paragraph
定义5.1.1 (极值点)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

定义在
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

上, 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}\in I$
\end_inset

, 若存在
\begin_inset Formula $\delta>0$
\end_inset

, s.t.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)\ge f(x_{0}),\qquad\forall x\in(x_{0}-\delta,x_{0}+\delta)\cap I,
\]

\end_inset

则称
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

上的极小值点, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x_{0})$
\end_inset

称为极小值.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}\in I$
\end_inset

, 且
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in I$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)\ge f(x_{0})$
\end_inset

, 则称
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在区间
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

上的最小值点, 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x_{0})$
\end_inset

称为函数
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在区间
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

上的最小值.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
定理5.1.1 (Fermat定理)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

上的极值点, 且
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

是内点, 若
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

处可导, 则
\begin_inset Formula $f'(x_{0})=0$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
注:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于极值点定义是在
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0}-\delta,x_{0}+\delta)\cap I$
\end_inset

上给出的, 所以以上定理要加上
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

是内点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
证明:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
使用极限的保号性, 判断
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f'(x_{0})=\lim_{x\to x_{0}^{-}}\frac{f(x)-f(x_{0})}{x-x_{0}}=\lim_{x\to x_{0}^{+}}\frac{f(x)-f(x_{0})}{x-x_{0}}
\]

\end_inset

的符号.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
满足
\begin_inset Formula $f'(x_{0})=0$
\end_inset

的点称为
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

的驻点, 临界点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若
\begin_inset Formula $f'(x_{0})\ge0$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\exists\delta>0$
\end_inset

, s.t.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in(x_{0}-\delta,x_{0}+\delta)$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula $(x-x_{0})(f(x)-f(x_{0}))\ge0$
\end_inset

, 但
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

附近不单调.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
定理5.1.2 (Darboux)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $[a,b]$
\end_inset

上的可导函数, 则
\begin_inset Formula $f'$
\end_inset

可以取到
\begin_inset Formula $f'_{+}(a)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $f'_{-}(b)$
\end_inset

之间的任意值.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
证明:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

介于
\begin_inset Formula $f'_{+}(a)$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $f'_{-}(b)$
\end_inset

之间, 定义
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)=f(x)-kx$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g'_{+}(a)g'_{-}(b)=(f'_{+}(a)-k)(f'_{-}(b)-k)\le0.
\]

\end_inset

若上式等于零, 命题显然.
 若上式小于零, 不妨设
\begin_inset Formula $g'_{+}(a)>0$
\end_inset

, 此时
\begin_inset Formula $x=a$
\end_inset

不是最大值点; 并有
\begin_inset Formula $g'_{-}(b)<0$
\end_inset

, 此时
\begin_inset Formula $x=b$
\end_inset

不是最大值点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
从而
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

只能在
\begin_inset Formula $[a,b]$
\end_inset

内取到最大值, 由Fermat定理, 存在
\begin_inset Formula $\xi\in(a,b)$
\end_inset

, s.t.
 
\begin_inset Formula $g'(\xi)=0$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
注:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
导函数有介值定理, 但导函数可以不连续, 比如
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}\sin\frac{1}{x}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in[-\pi,\pi]$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Darboux定理说明, 若
\begin_inset Formula $g'$
\end_inset

在任何点处不为零, 则
\begin_inset Formula $g'$
\end_inset

不变号.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Darboux定理的使用条件必须是区间内每点处可导.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
