, (
\begin_inset Formula $0<\eta<1$
\end_inset

), s.t.
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{R_{n}(x)}{(x-x_{0})^{n+1}}=\frac{F(x)-F(x_{0})}{G(x)-G(x_{0})}=\frac{F'(\xi)}{G'(\xi)}.
