\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{+\infty}f(x)\ud x$
\end_inset

与
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{+\infty}g(x)\ud x$
\end_inset

同收敛.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $l=0$
\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{+\infty}g(x)\ud x$
\end_inset

收敛可以推出
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{+\infty}f(x)\ud x$
\end_inset

收敛.
