\begin_inset Formula $0\le f\le Mg$
\end_inset

不可省, 否则取
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=\left|\frac{\sin x}{x\ln x}\right|$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)=\frac{\sin x}{x}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $l=+\infty$
\end_inset

时, 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{+\infty}g(x)\ud x$
