定理 7.3.4 (Abel).
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果广义积分 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{+\infty}f(x)dx$
\end_inset

 收敛, 函数 
\begin_inset Formula $g(x)$
\end_inset

 在 
\begin_inset Formula $[a,+\infty)$
\end_inset

 中单调有界, 则积分 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{+\infty}f(x)g(x)dx$
\end_inset

 也收敛.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
pf.
 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

有界, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $\left|g(x)\right|\le c$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall x\in[a,+\infty)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\int f$
\end_inset

收敛, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $\forall\epsilon$
\end_inset

>0, 
\begin_inset Formula $\exists M>0$
\end_inset

, s.t.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall B>A>M$
