\begin_inset Formula $|x|<1$
\end_inset

 时原级数绝对收敛; 而 
\begin_inset Formula $|x|>1$
\end_inset

 时显然发散.
 
\begin_inset Formula $x=1$
\end_inset

 时级数条件收敛; 
\begin_inset Formula $x=-1$
\end_inset

 时级数发散.
\end_layout

